So once they found out the swimming pool I was 3 levels of extremely happy. So beside the swimming pool there was also a wine shop and when I went to them and we also had wine along with my friends then we swam for a few hours. After that we straight away went to the beach which is near to the race or Dan had a great time and memorable time.
